erent contributions. A simple method reduces\nthe contamination to a level of < 10% for redshifts z<1. We also clarify the\nrelation to recent work on measuring gravitational redshifts by stacking\nclusters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 5 Sep 2013 11:50:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 29 Apr 2014 12:44:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-05-08"}
